▫️1 oz Smith & cross
▫️.5 oz Pineapple rum
▫️.75 Luxardo aperitivo
▫️.75 oz Pineapple juice
▫️.5 oz lime juice
▫️.25 oz maple syrup
▫️Shake ingredients with ice for 10 seconds. Pour over 🧊and garnish with lime and #luxardo cherry
